to learn a foreign language online.

17
00:00:48,032 --> 00:00:50,994
That's Duo, our green owl mascot that you'll see a lot

18
00:00:51,034 --> 00:00:52,255
in this presentation today.

19
00:00:53,255 --> 00:00:55,556
I had the privilege of joining Duolingo in 2012,

20
00:00:56,757 --> 00:00:58,658
three months after Duolingo's public launch.

21
00:00:59,398 --> 00:01:03,720
